metadata.name: RED
metadata.description: Red is a color that commands attention, symbolizing strong emotions such as passion, love, and anger. It has the power to grab the viewer's attention, evoking a sense of energy and excitement. It is used to highlight certain elements or to create contrast, red is a color that demands to be seen and cannot be ignored.
